text: The 1966–67 season was Cardiff City F.C.'s 40th season in the Football League. They competed in the 22-team Division Two, then the second tier of English football, finishing twentieth. ==Players== ==League standings== ==See also== *Cardiff City F.C. seasons ==References== * * *Welsh Football Data Archive Category:Cardiff City F.C. seasons Cardiff City Card
